               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-113ra)
 -
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-5rb)
 - Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols.
                     22rb-28rb)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from
                     Jerusalem” (fols. 28va-36vb)
 - Excerpt from Mawāśǝʾt (fols. 41ra-42ra;
                     61va-62va; 77ra)
 - Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests
                     and deacons (fols. 82ra-85ra)
 - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of
                     Ethiopia (fols. 91vb-94rb)
 - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols.
                     100ra-103rb)
 - Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fol. 103rb-103vb)
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
